# Literature PDFs — held locally under data/literature/<key>/<key>.pdf,
# not committed (publisher-formatted PDFs and group-internal theses).
# Extraction artefacts (extracted.yaml, notes.md) are tracked.
data/literature/**/*.pdf

# Local working drafts — person-to-person correspondence kept out of the
# repo. The sanitized, shareable public version lives at
# docs/architectures/bbo-coating-brief.md.
logbook/2026-05-20-bbo-coating-run-wp/expert-review-request-DRAFT.md

# Private outreach / correspondence logs — vendor and collaborator
# contact records. Local-only; never published to the site or committed.
/outreach/

# Lab-note Evernote exports (.enex) and their extracted binary attachments
# (photos, plots, vendor PDFs) are large and may hold unpublished material —
# kept local-only. The converted Markdown *text* under "data/lab notes/" IS
# committed (see data/lab notes/*.md).
/data/lab notes/*.enex
/data/lab notes/*.attachments/
